{
  "stem": "10859.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was not because she was the kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Usually, the people in Poland before the war-- we're talking about 50, 60 years ago-- if a husband or wife died, they never remarried.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just lived like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she worked very hard in the fields, took care of the cow, to get milk always from the cow, take care of the chickens.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was very religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because not only she, everybody was religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was not a question who is reformed, who is conservative, who is Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody was Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There wasn't the other kind of groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody was religious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You knew he has to get up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He has to go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He has to go in the evening in this synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sabbath, there's no question.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Everybody was in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You didn't have to wait for the high holidays, Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kippur, to go to the holidays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, when you're young, you really don't think about those things too much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we got suddenly hit, you know, with the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we didn't think about religion too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But everybody was born religiously and was raised religiously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's the way we lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Probably, if Hitler wouldn't have come and killed them, probably they would have been still today over there living that way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean aware of what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were very much concerned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to talk about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to get together, like, in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the only place, the only club, we used to get together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to talk about what happened, that year Hitler came to power and this.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
